# Epic Economics Website Environment Variables

# Google reCAPTCHA v3 Configuration
# Get your keys from: https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create
REACT_APP_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY=your_recaptcha_site_key_here
RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY=your_recaptcha_secret_key_here

# Resend Email Service (Recommended for Vercel)
# Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env.local
# 2. Replace the placeholder values with your actual keys
# 3. Never commit .env.local to version control

# To get reCAPTCHA keys:
# 1. Go to https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create
# 2. Choose reCAPTCHA v3
# 3. Add your domain(s): localhost (for development) and your production domain
# 4. Copy the Site Key to REACT_APP_RECAPTCHA_SITE_KEY
# 5. Copy the Secret Key to RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY (for backend verification)

# To get Resend API key:
# 1. Go to https://resend.com and sign up
# 2. Verify your domain or use the free resend.dev domain
# 3. Go to API Keys and create a new key
# 4. Copy the key to RESEND_API_KEY

# Add to your production environment (Vercel):
# 1. Go to your Vercel project dashboard
# 2. Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Add all three keys (mark RECAPTCHA_SECRET_KEY and RESEND_API_KEY as sensitive)
